The paper focuses on an infrastructure (DECREE) that aims to improve the reproducibility, practicality, and reusability of mobile-app analysis and instrumentation techniques. This topic falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and cybersecurity (cs.CR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the construction and execution of replication studies, which is relevant to programming languages (cs.PL) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper's potential to alter how research is conducted in this area suggests a focus on software engineering (cs.SE).
